Okhulumela abezimo eziphuthumayo kwa-ER24, uMnuz Russel Meiring, uthe bafike kulo muzi nozakwabo bakwaLife Healthcare ngo-11.20 sekukhona amaphoyisa. UMeiring uthe indoda namadodana ayo amabili eyodwa eneminyaka eyisishiyagalombili neneminyaka emine bebelele benganyakazi phakathi endlini. “Abezomthetho bavule umuzi bangena phakathi, okwenze abezimo eziphuthumayo bathatha iziguli bazikhiphela ngaphandle bazifaka kuma-ambulensi abelinde egcekeni,” kusho uMeiring. Uthe ngesikhathi sebengaphandle, baxilonge iziguli kwatholakala ukuthi isimo sibucayi. Kuthiwa abezimo eziphuthumayo basebenze kanzima bebahlenga bagcina sebexhunywa imishini yokuphefumula base bephuthunyiswa esibhedlela iNkosi Albert Luthuli ngendiza enophephela emhlane UMeiring uthe ayaziwa imbangela yesigameko kodwa abezomthetho bebekhona endaweni yesigameko beqhuba upheyo lwabo. Omakhelwane abebebukeka bekhungathekile bebemi egcekeni ngenkathi abezimo eziphuthumayo behlenga impilo yabadle ushevu. 